{"tid":1589291,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"林奠有話兒 - 陳也","createTime":"2019-09-23T08:25:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T08:25:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3e61c30f97491360141bdce4fab29b0729f53742","tid":1589291,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:25:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20190923/20773154\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190923%2F20773154&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK6%2BDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=da6be9e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190923%2F20773154&h=c7304453\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20190923/20773154</a><br />\n<br />\n林奠有話兒 - 陳也<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190923/large/1569148940_8604.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190923%2Flarge%2F1569148940_8604.jpg&h=6bcd22ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林奠對話會，有乜偈傾？<br />\n<br />\n一，你會用鐳射槍抑或餐刀切月餅？（明明冇差佬用鐳射筆照佢對眼，林奠依然眼眉跳，不停眨眼。）<br />\n<br />\n二，你撐三萬暴警，幾時幫OT的差佬提供free sex？（黑警對被補女示威者講過，因為被迫OT所以要強姦佢。林奠雖然冇耳仔聽，但fact check叻過羅范，考慮回應柒大慾求。）<br />\n<br />\n三，太子站831打死人疑團未解，你幾時落去B出口慰問入閘機？（即刻黑面的林奠一邊飲水一邊諗，係都去馬會慰勞馬主，叫他們x祿，死馬當活馬醫。）<br />\n<br />\n四，馬冇得照跑但舞照跳，工聯會麥美娟曾經當面X你，你會跳佢老舞嗎？（肥媽上身，呀呀呀呀&hellip;）<br />\n<br />\n五，你唔中意摘鉅摘楷，齋like摘瓜，有乜心得？（自稱最中意睇烹飪書的林奠變身大廚，柒婆賣瓜，摘完自誇，猛煮一百日的餸，名為香港瓜老襯。）<br />\n<br />\n六，唔該講人話，你想點死？（攬住磗頭跳海？飛鵝山吊頸？吩咐福建幫斬你九碌？密室獨食催淚彈？與何妖死亡之吻？） <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n咪執輸啦！！ (尊子)"}]}